-- Anglo Platinum to Boost Production by 100,000 Ounces in 2011 From Year Ago
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2011-02-07T07:12:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-07/anglo-platinum-to-boost-production-by-100-000-ounces-in-2011-from-year-ago.html
  Anglo Platinum Ltd . said it plans to
refine and sell 2.6 million ounces of the precious metal in
2011, an increase of 100,000 ounces over 2010, which it said
will be enough to meet its estimates of demand.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
